  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A peaceful morning stroll has turned into the deadliest day of your life.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398950/extras/f2499049c5d23f71d030e4afc6024ed6.avif?t=1748314354\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398950/extras_big/f2499049c5d23f71d030e4afc6024ed6.avif?t=1748314354 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a young woman living in a bucolic, peaceful Slavic village who is thrust into an apocalyptic scenario: a doomsday attack on her home. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398950/extras/98742d927f156efa9556e90383a1196d.avif?t=1748314354\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398950/extras_big/98742d927f156efa9556e90383a1196d.avif?t=1748314354 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Running seems to be the only survivable option.<br>The dark depths of the nearby woods hide an even darker secret. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398950/extras/38e4186902ebda678f4d28b8c3a9249e.avif?t=1748314354\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398950/extras_big/38e4186902ebda678f4d28b8c3a9249e.avif?t=1748314354 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An encounter with a mysterious beast of a man in the woods leaves you in a heart-racing predicament. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398950/extras/5af680141bad0f5c924538b315f8daec.avif?t=1748314354\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398950/extras_big/5af680141bad0f5c924538b315f8daec.avif?t=1748314354 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you find a way to escape him?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or will you learn how to dig deeper, and earn the man's trust instead? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Choose a side; Don't look back.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>There's more to find, than meets the eye.</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A peaceful morning stroll has turned into the deadliest day of your life.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398950/extras/f2499049c5d23f71d030e4afc6024ed6.avif?t=1748314354\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398950/extras_big/f2499049c5d23f71d030e4afc6024ed6.avif?t=1748314354 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a young woman living in a bucolic, peaceful Slavic village who is thrust into an apocalyptic scenario: a doomsday attack on her home. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398950/extras/98742d927f156efa9556e90383a1196d.avif?t=1748314354\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398950/extras_big/98742d927f156efa9556e90383a1196d.avif?t=1748314354 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Running seems to be the only survivable option.<br>The dark depths of the nearby woods hide an even darker secret. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398950/extras/38e4186902ebda678f4d28b8c3a9249e.avif?t=1748314354\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398950/extras_big/38e4186902ebda678f4d28b8c3a9249e.avif?t=1748314354 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An encounter with a mysterious beast of a man in the woods leaves you in a heart-racing predicament. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398950/extras/5af680141bad0f5c924538b315f8daec.avif?t=1748314354\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398950/extras_big/5af680141bad0f5c924538b315f8daec.avif?t=1748314354 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you find a way to escape him?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or will you learn how to dig deeper, and earn the man's trust instead? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Choose a side; Don't look back.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>There's more to find, than meets the eye.</i></p>",
